****    drm-dkms    ****

Steps needed in order to build a drm backport.

 - Grab the release you want from http://drvbp1.linux-foundation.org/~mcgrof/rel-html/backports/
 - rm -r $package_root/backports
 - extract backport package as $package_root/backports/
 - Disable unneeded patches in debian/patches
 - Bump version in debian/changelog
 - Build and install
-> profit
